author: wn.com
title: Labor to support China Free Trade Agreement after months of concerns
text: Labor's caucus has voted to approve the Chinese Free Trade deal after negotiating some technical changes with the Government. Labor says they've won important legal safeguards for workers, but the Government says it won't change the free trade agreement as signed with the Chinese government. ...
